#
# Traffic Shaping filter (HTTP/HTTPS - 1Mbps, other - 256 Kbps)
# 
# *** Every single filter must have this loophole to our static content
pass in proto tcp to 194.67.1.117 port eq 80,443
pass out proto tcp from 194.67.1.117 port eq 80,443
# ***
# *** Every upfilter must have blocking to dev Auth service
block in proto tcp to 194.67.1.39
block out proto tcp from 194.67.1.39
# ***
# requested by Beeline RfC 271381/12
block in proto tcp to 194.67.1.38
block out proto tcp from 194.67.1.38
shape rate 1024 in proto tcp to port eq 80,443
shape rate 1024 out proto tcp from port eq 80,443
shape rate 256 in
shape rate 256 out
